short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Insert a custom Element into Infinity Craft

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Have you ever wanted to make something in Infinite Craft, but are to lazy to merge things together to get it? This extension solves this problem by giving you a easy interface to insert a fully custom Element.
